is a big enough chunk
of W1 steel

05:10.519 --> 05:11.978
<i>to make the hardenable blade,</i>

05:11.978 --> 05:14.981
<i>and then I need two pieces</i>
<i>of the soft, mild steel</i>

05:14.981 --> 05:16.483
so I can complete
the San Mai weld.

05:16.483 --> 05:19.486
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:19.486 --> 05:21.738
‐ Marine Corps always teams up.
Band of brothers.

05:24.491 --> 05:25.659
‐ There we go.

05:25.659 --> 05:27.202
<i>‐ We're gonna attack</i>
<i>this anchor</i>

05:27.202 --> 05:29.830
