every man for himself.

05:52.894 --> 05:55.021
All right.
Take these over to the grinder.

05:55.021 --> 05:56.565
<i>The first thing</i>
<i>that I'm gonna do is</i>

05:56.565 --> 05:59.109
<i>take the two mild pieces</i>
<i>of steel, clean it up.</i>

05:59.109 --> 06:00.193
<i>♪ ♪</i>

