06:34.603 --> 06:35.896
<i>Started going at it.</i>

06:35.896 --> 06:37.772
Immediately I can tell
that I got a good weld.

06:37.772 --> 06:39.232
I think I'm good to go.

06:39.232 --> 06:40.567
<i>♪ ♪</i>

06:40.567 --> 06:42.485
‐ We've given these guys
unfamiliar tools,

06:42.485 --> 06:44.029
unfamiliar forge,

06:44.029 --> 06:46.990
