06:53.622 --> 06:56.958
<i>‐ My game plan for this is</i>
<i>I don't want any mild steel</i>

06:56.958 --> 06:58.752
<i>down near my edge</i>
<i>or my bevels,</i>

06:58.752 --> 07:01.129
