thin strips of mild steel,

07:01.129 --> 07:02.422
<i>one on each side</i>

07:02.422 --> 07:04.257
<i>to my hardenable steel</i>
<i>just to jacket it,</i>

07:04.257 --> 07:05.842
<i>and we'll forge weld</i>
<i>that together.</i>

07:05.842 --> 07:08.928
That way meet parameters
