07:32.952 --> 07:34.663
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:34.663 --> 07:36.498
‐ Hot metal.

07:36.498 --> 07:39.125
<i>I draw my three pieces</i>
<i>of metal out</i>

07:39.125 --> 07:42.253
and I realize my two pieces
of mild steel,

07:42.253 --> 07:45.006
they're not as long
as the hard W1 steel.

07:45.006 --> 07:46.716
Doggone it.

07:46.716 --> 07:48.426
‐ On a thick centerpiece,

07:48.426 --> 07:49.886
