and cool quicker.

07:51.971 --> 07:53.556
Don't necessarily
weld very well.

07:53.556 --> 07:54.933
<i>‐ I'm running out of time,</i>

07:54.933 --> 07:58.019
<i>so I'm going to the press</i>
<i>to do my forge weld.</i>

07:58.019 --> 08:00.063
