08:04.484 --> 08:06.319
‐ She ain't gonna be pretty.

08:06.319 --> 08:08.988
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:08.988 --> 08:11.074
<i>‐ I've got my three pieces</i>
<i>of steel together.</i>

08:11.074 --> 08:12.867
I'm drawing the steel out.

08:12.867 --> 08:14.869
‐ Now Rick's starting
to move some metal.

08:14.869 --> 08:16.162
‐ Woop, woop, woop.

08:16.162 --> 08:18.665
