08:20.333 --> 08:21.751
Nope, not good enough.

08:21.751 --> 08:23.837
‐ It looks like those two
pieces have kind of smeared.

08:23.837 --> 08:25.213
‐ Are moving.

08:25.213 --> 08:27.006
‐ What the hell's going on
with this thing?

08:27.006 --> 08:28.842
Right now, I don't have
any time to restart.

08:28.842 --> 08:31.428
I have to keep pushing forward,

08:31.428 --> 08:33.221
<i>so I'm just gonna keep on</i>
<i>drawing this billet out</i>

08:33.221 --> 08:35.640
