08:39.602 --> 08:42.647
‐ It's an obstacle,
but as a marine,

08:42.647 --> 08:45.025
I'm gonna push through
and I'm gonna make it past it.

08:45.025 --> 08:46.609
That looks better, okay.

08:46.609 --> 08:49.738
Looks like a majority of
the billet is, in fact, welded.

08:49.738 --> 08:51.531
Thank you, all right.

08:51.531 --> 08:53.825
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:55.785 --> 08:57.454
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:57.454 --> 08:58.872
<i>I get the blade</i>
<i>roughly shaped,</i>

08:58.872 --> 09:00.206
<i>I get over to the grinder.</i>

09:00.206 --> 09:01.583
